                <p>The Linux Kernel has a bug affecting containers which requires a reboot to resolve.  The Carina team will start rebooting all Carina instances on <strong>Monday at Noon CST</strong>.  This process will take approximately 90 minutes.  Users will not have access to their instances during this time. Please make sure to check restart settings and backup your data.</p>
                <p>We will provide up to the minute updates during the maintenance window on our [status page](https://carinabyrackspace.statuspage.io/).</p>
